"Rubrication","#execution.rubrication",{"lettering":39,"dimensions":40},"Tall, slightly curved letters, mostly with minimal serifs. P is open; R is closed with long tail; E has short horizontals of equal length, slightly upward curving; M is four equal slanting strokes. In line 5 the O and C of 'procos' are intelinked, and the following O is small and mid-line. A large diagonal upward stroke is visible above the first letter of each of the civic ethnics; and a horizontal above the Q at the end of line 6. The letters all show traces of dark paint (modern?).",[41,49,55,60,66,71,75,80,86,91,93,97,101],{"type":42,"l":43,"from":44,"to":44,"h":45,"unit":46,"atLeast":47,"atMost":48},"letterHeight","Line 1","line1","65-71","mm","65","71",{"type":42,"l":50,"from":51,"to":51,"h":52,"unit":46,"atLeast":53,"atMost":54},"Line 2","line2","68-74","68","74",{"type":42,"l":56,"from":57,"to":57,"h":58,"unit":46,"atLeast":59,"atMost":54},"Line 3","line3","70-74","70",{"type":42,"l":61,"from":62,"to":62,"h":63,"unit":46,"atLeast":64,"atMost":65},"Line 4","line4","72-75","72","75",{"type":42,"l":67,"from":68,"to":68,"h":69,"unit":46,"atLeast":70,"atMost":64},"Line 5","line5","67-72","67",{"type":42,"l":72,"from":73,"to":73,"h":74,"unit":46,"atLeast":70,"atMost":54},"Line 6","line6","67-74",{"type":42,"l":76,"from":77,"to":77,"h":78,"unit":46,"atLeast":54,"atMost":79},"Line 7","line7","74-78","78",{"type":81,"l":82,"from":44,"to":51,"h":83,"unit":46,"atLeast":84,"atMost":85},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","50-52","50","52",{"type":81,"l":87,"from":51,"to":57,"h":88,"unit":46,"atLeast":89,"atMost":90},"Interlineation line 2 to 3","47-51","47","51",{"type":81,"l":92,"from":57,"to":62,"h":83,"unit":46,"atLeast":84,"atMost":85},"Interlineation line 3 to 4",{"type":81,"l":94,"from":62,"to":68,"h":95,"unit":46,"atLeast":84,"atMost":96},"Interlineation line 4 to 5","50-53","53",{"type":81,"l":98,"from":68,"to":73,"h":99,"unit":46,"atLeast":85,"atMost":100},"Interlineation line 5 to 